  "detailed_description": "Keo and the Cosmic Crystals is a 2D platform game with colorful and cute graphics, featuring high difficulty and precision challenges.<br><br>In this game, you control Keo, an 8-year-old boy who, after noticing colorful crystals falling from the skies, decided to embark on an adventure in search of the mysterious Cosmic Crystals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553590/extras/4b006f7c7a7d0d4a7aac80b090eece51.poster.avif?t=1738391688\" width=320 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553590/extras/4b006f7c7a7d0d4a7aac80b090eece51.webm?t=1738391688\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553590/extras/4b006f7c7a7d0d4a7aac80b090eece51.mp4?t=1738391688\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game features...<br><br>• Polished gameplay and controls<br>• High difficulty and exciting challenges<br>• Fun and infectious music!<br>• Beautiful retro-style graphics with vibrant and colorful colors<br>• 60 short and enjoyable levels<br>• 5 themes from different and creative worlds<br>• 4 challenging bosses<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2553590/extras/fc0458516121d2551d7ab0c9bde439fa.avif?t=1738391688\" width=320 height=320 /></span>",
